title: Nitzer Ebb - remixes of Showtime tracks
description:
A compact disc maxi-single (hey, that's what they called it) with several mixes of 3 tunes from 1990's Showtime album.


Lightning Man (The Industry vs. The Ebb Mix)     6:40   
Lightning Man (RSW Mix)     5:08   
Getting Closer (The Pool Mix)     5:21   
Getting Closer (The Trance Mix)     7:17   
Getting Closer (The Kitchen Mix)     5:08   
Fun To Be Had (Zulu Mix)     5:20   
Fun To Be Had (The George Clinton Mix/Long Mix)     7:14 


.wma format at a variable bit rate
